{"tid":2356063,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"薯伯伯：再次呼籲轉用 Signal — 它與 WhatsApp 的分別","createTime":"2021-01-06T14:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T17:19:23.000Z","uid":48083,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ec20ddc92c3cb6d61e1142cbd2d7da6bc03636e3","tid":2356063,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T14:03:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/technology/%E5%86%8D%E6%AC%A1%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E8%BD%89%E7%94%A8-signal/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ftechnology%2F%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E5%2591%25BC%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E8%25BD%2589%25E7%2594%25A8-signal%2F&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5sorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=2f2241c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ftechnology%2F%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E5%2591%25BC%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E8%25BD%2589%25E7%2594%25A8-signal%2F&h=e7c40e04\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/technology/%E5%86%8D%E6%AC%A1%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E8%BD%89%E7%94%A8-signal/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記得去年開始多人轉用 Signal 的時候，有人就經常說兩者相同，都有端對端加密，都要用電話號碼登記，而近來 WhatsApp 又跟隨 Signal 的後塵，可以開啟「限時訊息」。<br />\n<br />\n那麼為何仍然要轉用 Signal？<br />\n<br />\n這一張圖可以告知你答案。<br />\n<br />\n最近 Apple 要求開發商要主動申報 app 取得的私隱資料，大家看一看兩幅圖。<br />\n<br />\n左圖是 Signal 的申報，這個軟件取得關於你的資料是 0，取得非關連到你的資料就只有一個，電話號碼。一個有幾百萬人用的軟件，居然取得用戶關連的資料是零，這是業界最出色的典範。<br />\n<br />\n反觀 Facebook 旗下的 WhatsApp，其私隱申報長到嚇死人，如果你要放大圖像才看得清內容，可以自行去 AppStore 查看！WhatsApp 最近還改動了政策，講到明要同 Facebook 交流資料，你就是他們的產品了。<br />\n<br />\n保護自己，就是保護別人。<br />\n<br />\n驚係無用，我寧願無時無刻提醒自己，每日仍然有好多需要做的事情。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n作者 Patreon"},{"pid":"e34f09aceee5a546b4e6181c371f809d22cb5112","tid":2356063,"uid":264983,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已轉"},{"pid":"c6738e3d54b89c36c126fef35c2ad7c6429557d4","tid":2356063,"uid":89879,"like":11,"dislike":1,"sc